title: Unique 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Crescent Valley Home on Acreage
posting_body: ['Unique 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Crescent Valley Home on Acreage', 'This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom early 1900’s farm home has been updated and features a large property with beautiful old growth trees and foliage.', 'The three story home is approximately 2,000 sq.', 'ft, has an additional bonus room/den and a large rec room downstairs.', 'On the main floor is a spacious living room and dining room area with lots of natural light, one bedroom and a full bathroom.', 'Fireplace is for decorative use only.', 'There is a mudroom and a kitchen which includes a stainless refrigerator, dishwasher, oven and hood fan.', 'On the second level of the home is a large landing and 2 bedrooms.', 'The lower level has a utility room with W/D hookups only and a full bathroom.', ' This property is close to downtown Gig Harbor and down the block is Crescent Creek Park with baseball, tennis, basketball and sand volleyball courts.', ' This home has a covered front porch, a detached garage, and a separate deck area.', 'Partial yard care is included.', ' No Pets and No Smoking property.', 'Applications accepted only through McNally Management.', 'Apply at <URL>', '9820 Crescent Valley Drive', 'Gig Harbor, WA 98332', 'Rent: $2100', 'Deposit: $2000', 'Non-refundable Application Fee: $50.00/adult', '12 month lease', 'Available September 1st', 'Call for more information', 'McNally Management', 'show contact info']
